Notes on map :

When you play it you should see up in the air a big text saying "Made By Khallal", This is to make sure nobody else takes credit for the map.

The cloaks is a pretty "dark" and confusing spot. This is just to make "knifing" easier and getting shot unprepared, so you shit your pants :D 

If you upload this to a server or you just want to try it up. Make sure you write in console "buildcubemaps" and restart again.
